<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>عَلَيْهِمْ نارٌ مُؤْصَدَةٌ <span class="c2">(٢٠)</span><a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
